Abolished 1894 to become the separate parishes of Clase Urban 
    and Clase Rural.

Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of Clase. Abolished 
    9.11.1918 and divided between the parishes of Swansea and Llangyfelach.

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Clase in Swansea County 
    Borough. Abolished 26.3.1900 and added to the parish of Swansea.

Created 1894 from the rural parts of the parish of Swansea Higher 
    & Lower. Abolished 9.11.1918 and added to the parish of Swansea.

Created 9.11.1918 from the parishes of Penderry and Clase Rural. 
    See also Table 2, note (e).

Created 1.4.1905 from the parishes of Llansamlet Higher and Llansamlet 
    Lower. Abolished 9.11.1918 and added to the parish of Swansea.

Abolished 1.4.1905 and added to the parish of Llansamlet. 
    See also Table 2, note (c).

Abolished 1.4.1905 and added to the parish of Llansamlet.
